  "detailed_description": "Shadow Hunter is a casual deductive puzzle game with RPG elements.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/365270/extras/8fc8608fd82799f27f50f258b5bb0647.avif?t=1466908459\" width=80 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/365270/extras/d8cef9a21bf84f9324bd4d5f6f06eeff.avif?t=1466908459\" width=80 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/365270/extras/d11456ebc10976c8bafebb2ea2e22dc3.avif?t=1466908459\" width=80 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/365270/extras/49ae92c8c4e1ce20d8db500dcc3921fc.avif?t=1466908459\" width=80 height=80 /></span><br><br>As a Shadow Hunter, you must use your senses to detect dangers and artifacts beneath the endless darkness that spreads throughout the land.  Anti-light, the dimension and dimensional darkness from beyond the void gate, threatens to swallow us all. You must quest to find the Shadow Gate Fragments, to destroy the Anti-light menace.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>16 areas to explore.<br></li><li>Deductive mini-games.<br></li><li>Random events.<br></li><li>Local high-score list.<br></li><li>Great horror atmosphere.<br></li><li>Turn-based.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Shadow Hunter is a casual deductive puzzle game with RPG elements.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/365270/extras/8fc8608fd82799f27f50f258b5bb0647.avif?t=1466908459\" width=80 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/365270/extras/d8cef9a21bf84f9324bd4d5f6f06eeff.avif?t=1466908459\" width=80 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/365270/extras/d11456ebc10976c8bafebb2ea2e22dc3.avif?t=1466908459\" width=80 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/365270/extras/49ae92c8c4e1ce20d8db500dcc3921fc.avif?t=1466908459\" width=80 height=80 /></span><br><br>As a Shadow Hunter, you must use your senses to detect dangers and artifacts beneath the endless darkness that spreads throughout the land.  Anti-light, the dimension and dimensional darkness from beyond the void gate, threatens to swallow us all. You must quest to find the Shadow Gate Fragments, to destroy the Anti-light menace.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>16 areas to explore.<br></li><li>Deductive mini-games.<br></li><li>Random events.<br></li><li>Local high-score list.<br></li><li>Great horror atmosphere.<br></li><li>Turn-based.</li></ul>",
